== Usage ==
This template allows for convenient linking to the Gatherer Lookup page (Wizards of the Coast's official database search engine) for cards from ''[[万智牌|Magic: The Gathering]]''.  The template supports linking to cards by name and by Gatherer-assigned ID number (found at the end of each card edition's URL), allowing for general and edition-specific releases.

Note that in articles, this template should only be used in the External links section (see [[Wikipedia:外部链接|Wikipedia:External links]] for more information).

A short template name, <nowiki>{{mtgcard}}</nowiki>, may be used.


For example, '''<nowiki>{{mtgcard|Wrath of God}}</nowiki>''' produces:

{{mtgcard|Wrath of God}}


While, '''<nowiki>{{mtgcard|Wrath of God|2373}}</nowiki>''' produces the Fourth Edition release:

{{mtgcard|Wrath of God|2373}}


The name of the card is not required for the template to work,

Writing, '''<nowiki>{{mtgcard||2373}}</nowiki>''' produces:

{{mtgcard||2373}}


Excluding both name and ID number results in a link to the Gatherer Lookup home page,

Writing, '''<nowiki>{{mtgcard||}}</nowiki>''' produces:

{{mtgcard||}}

